description: Dashboard for Spring Boot2.1 Statistics(based on Spring Boot2 Statistic by micrometer-prometheus).

targets.expr: irate(http_server_requests_seconds_sum{instance="$instance", application="${application.title}", job="$job", exception="None", uri!~"root|.*actuator.*|/\\*\\*"}[5m]) / irate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{instance="$instance", application="${application.title}", job="$job", exception="None", uri!~"root|.*actuator.*|/\\*\\*"}[5m])

(irate(http_server_requests_seconds_sum{instance="$instance", job="$job", application="${application.title}", exception="None", uri!~"root|.*actuator.*|/\\*\\*"}[5m]) / irate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{instance="$instance", application="${application.title}", job="$job", exception="None", uri!~"root|.*actuator.*|/\\*\\*"}[5m]))>29

alert.message: Please check, too many errors on NboTool
alert.name: ERROR logs alert
